Subject: [PATCH 3/7] Allow building without inotify support


diff --git a/configure.ac b/configure.ac
index 1111111..2222222 100644
--- a/configure.ac
+++ b/configure.ac
@@ -1698,10 +1698,16 @@ dnl *****************************
 dnl ** Check for inotify (GIO) **
 dnl *****************************
